Hello! A luzak will always have orange bulbs (berries?) on the tree. On a luzak the first two can be any color but the bulbs are always orange But remember, like I said, if the leaves are also orange than it doesn't matter that the bulbs are orange, it isn't a luzak.
the luzak has a purple or green trunk but always gold berries.

This one was really hard.  I'm not 100 percent sure on it.  It looks like a tree with leaves and it has little round balls on it that I think all should be orange.  It doesn't seem to matter what colors the leaves or the trunk of the tree are.
if the berries are orange and the trunk/base is anything EXCEPT orange then choose it

The lulaz is the tree with orange berries, the color of the trunk and leaves are irrelevant. However, when the tree doesn't have leaves, orange and red berries look kind of similar so take care in that regard

the creatures look like trees, with a trunk, leaves and berries. a luzek has orange berries and a trunk that is NOT WHITE.  so find all the ones with orange berries and then if the trunk is a color that isn't white, it's a luzek
they have to have leaves and a purple trunk.
only purple, green, orange trunk with orange berries together
